<h2>Action Required: Reconnect Your <%= @store.platform.titleize %> Store</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @user.first_name.presence || 'there' %>,</p>

<p>We've detected an issue with the connection to your <%= @store.platform.titleize %> store <strong><%= @store.name %></strong>.</p>

<p>Your store's API credentials appear to be invalid or expired. This can happen if:</p>
<ul style="margin: 16px 0; line-height: 1.8; color: #303030;">
  <li>You've uninstalled and reinstalled the Framefox Connect app</li>
  <li>Your <%= @store.platform.titleize %> access token has been revoked</li>
  <li>There have been changes to your store's permissions</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>What this means:</strong></p>
<p style="margin: 8px 0 24px 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #6b7280;">
  Until you reconnect your store, we won't be able to sync products, process orders, or update variant images for this store.
</p>

<p>To restore the connection, please reconnect your store:</p>

<div class="btn-wrapper">
  <%= link_to "Reconnect #{@store.platform.titleize} Store", connections_root_url, class: "btn" %>
</div>

<p style="margin: 32px 0 0 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
  Once you're signed in, you'll be able to reconnect your store through the platform connections page.
</p>

<p style="margin: 32px 0 0 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
  If you're experiencing issues or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.
</p>

<p style="margin: 24px 0 0 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #303030;">
  Best regards,<br>
  The Framefox Team
</p>

